    <item>
      <title>美国原油、汽油库存下降提供一定支撑，油价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rebounds-us-crude-gasoline-stockpile-drops-provide-some-support-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在前一交易日下跌后于周四反弹，原因是美国原油和汽油库存下降支撑了市场，此前有迹象表明美联储可能会在更长时间内维持较高利率，这抑制了未来燃料需求的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rebounds-us-crude-gasoline-stockpile-drops-provide-some-support-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:07:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着就业复苏，澳大利亚二月份失业率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-jobless-rate-dives-feb-employment-resurgent-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚就业人数在 2 月份大幅反弹，而失业率则远低于预期，这明显表明劳动力市场仍然紧张，而且近期的疲软状况在统计上被夸大了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-jobless-rate-dives-feb-employment-resurgent-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，Shein 将向全球品牌推销供应链基础设施</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-market-supply-chain-infrastructure-global-brands-wsj-reports-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》周三援引执行主席唐唐致投资者的一封信报道称，中国成立的快时尚公司 Shein 将向全球品牌提供其供应链基础设施和技术。]]></description>
