      <title>日本央行行长誓言维持货币刺激，支持物价上涨势头</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-chief-vows-support-economy-with-monetary-stimulus-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫周四誓言将继续以超宽松货币政策支持经济，但暗示信心通胀正在增强，市场正在寻找下次加息时机的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-chief-vows-support-economy-with-monetary-stimulus-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:46:26 GMT</pubDate>
