      <title>日本工厂活动缓慢下滑，服务业回升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-factory-activity-declines-slow-service-sector-picks-up-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四的一项商业调查显示，日本 3 月份工厂活动萎缩速度放缓，而服务业的进一步扩张支撑了私营部门的整体增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-factory-activity-declines-slow-service-sector-picks-up-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:42:10 GMT</pubDate>
