      <title>英特尔准备在美国四个州投入 1000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-prepares-100-bln-spending-spree-across-four-us-states-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在获得 195 亿美元的联邦拨款和贷款后，英特尔正计划在美国四个州投入 1000 亿美元，用于建设和扩建工厂，并希望获得另外 250 亿美元的税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-prepares-100-bln-spending-spree-across-four-us-states-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 09:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
